WEBVTT

00:00:01.459 --> 00:00:07.459
The Good News according to Jesus series is now available in JW Library.

00:00:07.459 --> 00:00:13.460
See the Gospels come alive by viewing video clips as you study the Bible.

00:00:13.460 --> 00:00:16.460
Want to learn how?

00:00:16.460 --> 00:00:22.460
In the Library tab, go to convention releases and select day three.

00:00:22.460 --> 00:00:25.460
There you'll find a new publication.

00:00:25.460 --> 00:00:30.460
The Good News according to Jesus' Video Reference Guide.

00:00:30.460 --> 00:00:35.460
Download this publication to see a scene by scene breakdown of each episode

00:00:35.460 --> 00:00:39.460
and references to the verses on which each scene is based.

00:00:39.460 --> 00:00:46.049
Once you've downloaded the Good News Video Reference Guide,

00:00:46.049 --> 00:00:52.049
you can access video clips directly from your Bible in JW Library.

00:00:52.049 --> 00:00:54.049
Tap on a verse.

00:00:54.049 --> 00:00:59.049
Then tap on the Gem icon to see the study content for the verse,

00:00:59.049 --> 00:01:04.049
including clips from the Good News series as they become available.

00:01:04.049 --> 00:01:08.049
If supported on your device, use the Picture and Picture feature

00:01:08.049 --> 00:01:12.049
to view the Bible and video at the same time.

00:01:12.049 --> 00:01:17.049
Bring your Bible reading to life with these new features.
